
check-dns-availability
**********************


DESCRIPTION
===========

Checks if the specified CNAME is available.


SYNOPSIS
========

   aws elasticbeanstalk check-dns-availability
     --cname-prefix <value>


REQUIRED PARAMETERS
===================

"--cname-prefix"  (string)
   The prefix used when this CNAME is reserved.


OPTIONAL PARAMETERS
===================

None
